      "channelId": "5a29faf1-6466-4da8-a62c-bfd52faf2f82",
      "text": "Kiki negotiated with Stefan Kanalga from House of Trust to partner on Davos events; partnership focused on Christian wealth community; House of Trust offering presentation slots and worship day",
