      "channelId": "5a29faf1-6466-4da8-a62c-bfd52faf2f82",
      "text": "Sofia F provided detailed Davos fashion and logistics guide: matte textures, neutral colors, structured blazers, polished leather boots, silver jewelry; branded recommendations (The Row, Totême, Max Mara, COS)",
