      "channelId": "5a29faf1-6466-4da8-a62c-bfd52faf2f82",
      "text": "Sofia F documented Davos social geography: Congress Centre as inner circle hub; Promenade as main thoroughfare with government/corporate houses; hotels as mini-embassies with panels/dinners; Swedish lunch at mountain hotel Schatzalp signals inclusion in elite group",
