      "channelId": "5a29faf1-6466-4da8-a62c-bfd52faf2f82",
      "text": "Multiple accommodation plays: central 1-bed (4.3k CHF/5 nights), Klosters 15min away (13k CHF for 3 guests), Abraham House private room (5.2k CHF with badge package), Stephanie's apartment (2 payments of 2k each, Sunday-Friday)",
